OL,3,CFree music lessons for school pupils
OL,4,Ccould be lost in council cuts
OL,6,FOne pupil who took advantage of these
OL,7,Flessons is Ollie Thompson.
OL,9,FHe said: "I feel it'd be a big
OL,10,Fdisappointment to future pupils coming
OL,11,Finto the school system, who are
OL,12,Fwanting to get into an instrument.
OL,14,F"It would take away not only from the
OL,15,Fpupils, but the school community in
OL,16,Fgeneral."
OL,18,FRosie Smith has recently started
OL,19,Fukulele lessons.
