OL,3,CFree music lessons for school pupils
OL,4,Ccould be lost in council cuts
OL,6,FHer mum, Tammy, said: "So many
OL,7,Fchildren value music and for it to
OL,8,Fstart costing an extortionate amount
OL,9,Fof money would really put people
OL,10,Foff... because it's just not
OL,11,Faffordable at all."
OL,13,FOn her experience with lessons, Rosie
OL,14,Fsaid: "It's been amazing. My teacher,
OL,15,FMr. Taylor, is so, so kind... I've
OL,16,Flearnt so many songs."
