OL,3,CFree music lessons for school pupils
OL,4,Ccould be lost in council cuts
OL,6,FIt is not only individual lessons
OL,7,Funder threat, as Dumfries and Galloway
OL,8,FCouncil says the cuts may also mean
OL,9,Fschool bands and choirs could no
OL,10,Flonger continue.
OL,12,FMike Swale, chair of the Annan Town
OL,13,FBand, emphasised the demand for
OL,14,Flessons.
OL,16,FHe said: "At the moment, there's about
OL,17,F2000 kids having instrument
OL,18,Finstruction and around 700 on the
OL,19,Fwaiting list.
