OL,4,Ccould be lost in council cuts
OL,6,F"So there's a huge demand for it, and
OL,7,Fthey enjoy it. (The council) need find
OL,8,Fa way to save it somehow."
OL,10,FLeader of Dumfries and Galloway
OL,11,FCouncil, Cllr Stephen Thompson (SNP),
OL,12,Furged residents to make their views on
OL,13,Fthe proposals known.
OL,15,FHe said: "We know that people value
OL,16,Fthose services. It's just that we have
OL,17,Fto make choices and it's very, very
OL,18,Fdifficult.
