OL,6,F"So there's no doubt that, along with
OL,7,Fmany other proposals that have been
OL,8,Fput out, are going to get people
OL,9,Fworried because we know how much they
OL,10,Fuse and value that service.
OL,12,F"So I'd urge people who do use that
OL,13,Fservice to let us know just how
OL,14,Fimportant it is to them."
OL,16,FThe budget consultation will run until
OL,17,FSunday November 23.
